channel.title: How do i STart a server?
channel.description:
This Question is simple. How do i start/make a server? I want a plain RS2 Server only I start out super rich, Maxed out skills and no tutorial island. Can someone just give me the code? Please?
Ok people are being really rude so Let me refrase this.
Im a TOTAL newbie at this. I have NO programmin experience. I dont know how to start a server. I want to make a RS2 server like some others ive seen. Such as getting rich super easy and maxing out skills super easy. Also theres servers that have things like 3 Jads and a tele there. How do I make this? Where can I get the code?
